argin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br /></span></strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">都来找树洞吧</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">每晚<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n			style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(236, 30, 9); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">21:30~23:30</span></strong><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(236, 30, 9); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n			style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">等</span></span>你\r\n	</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', null, null, '2', '3', null);
INSERT INTO `detail` VALUES ('17', '写给19考研的经验回忆录', '1', '原哥工作室', '/upload/00000000029.jpg', '<section>\r\n	<p\r\n		style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n		<img class=\" __bg_gif\" title=\"1顶部横条.gif\" width=\"auto\"\r\n			src=\"/upload/00000000027.gif\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</section>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<p\r\n			style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 15px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 244); color: rgb(123, 123, 111); border-radius: 4px; width: 606.359px; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 244);\">\r\n			<span\r\n				style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px;\">先来讲一下人的经历，本人理科生，属于三跨考生，一战南开大学，专业课238，总分过线，但是外语成绩差南开外语线十几分遗憾落榜，因此选择工作，工作一年之后仍然想考研，于是辞去工作准备考研。</span>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">总分382，专业课253，日语56，政治73。我的考研准备时间是从17年6月份正式开始，最终决定考西北大学中国史专业，外语选择是日语。说一下各科的准备情况吧。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">&gt;&gt;&nbsp;专业课</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">每个人对于学习都有自己的方法，不必与别人相同，主要是找到适合自己的方法。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我认为对于历史学习最重要的是兴趣，兴趣能够激发你的学习潜力，同时能够在枯燥的准备过程中给你动力。在专业课的准备过程中，最重要的是要形成自己的答题套路、思考体系，这是别人无法给你的，同时也是考试时你自己的优势。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">考试时间有限，如何在有限的时间内答出体系较为完整、逻辑思路清晰的内容才是重中之重。不管前期准备多少知识，重要的是你能够在紧张的状态下将其发挥出来，这也是老师阅卷时所希望看到的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">18年考试题型</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">名词解释10选8（8*15分）、论述图4选3（3*45分）、阅读材料题（抄写+翻译+回答问题\r\n		1*45分）</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">参考书目</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">除去西北大学官网所要求的课本，我还看了张岂之先生的课本作为补充，不是说一定要看，如果有余力的话扩充一下自己的知识面是可以的，当然必须以一套课本为主，我当时是以西北大学官网所定教材为主进行复习。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">复习资料</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">主要以仝晰纲大本、我自己的名词解释、论述题记忆自己的历年真题整理为主。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">每天至少有4-5个小时的时间花在专业课上，我学习并不是十分努力，但是学习时非常注重思考、捋清思路，把书本知识变成自己的知识才是最重要的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">历年真题一定要好好利用，尽量自己能够独立的做一遍，这样就能够找出自己的不足与答题时的缺陷，完善真题答案，这样这些题就成为了自己的知识。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">当然也要注意其他学校的真题，兼取众长，吸收其中你认为好的题。同时在接近考试的一百天内，要注重考试模拟练习，这样能够让你更好地把握考试时间的分配与答题速度，也是模拟考试的氛围，让自己紧张起来。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">一定要注意考试时间，尽量能够答完题，如果题目都答不完，这相当于你做了一份不到300分的试卷，这与你的竞争者们相比，少了许多优势。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">千万要记住，这300分的专业课才是最重要的，不要过分在外语以及政治上下苦功夫，专业课的投入才是最重要的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">西北大学的考题范围广泛，涵盖了中国古代史、近代史以及现代史，同时还有一本文献学，这是不可忽视的。虽然名词解释是10选8，但是谁又能保证除去你放弃的那两个，其他的名词解释又能够答得非常完美，所以在复习课本时要做到细致全面。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">一个名词解释15分，分数并不低，所以要好好重视。论述题最重要的是答题系统、逻辑清晰，让阅卷老师在短时间内了解到你的答题内容，即使你的知识量很大但答题毫无章法并不能成为你的优势。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">&gt;&gt;外语</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我的外语选择是日语，本科从没接触过，因此我也是报了网课班，认认真真的做并翻译了真题两边，准备了一下作文模板。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">本次日语成绩一般，可能是理科生的弱项吧，因此也没有过多经验。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">&gt;&gt;政治</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">从暑假开始准备政治，每天1-2小时，进入9月份慢慢提高时间比重，降低日语学习时间。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我主要以政治大纲解析以及肖秀荣的题为主，后期以肖四为主，政治复习重在选择题，后面的大题除非你特别优秀，一般是无法拉开差距，因此要重视选择题。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">后面大题，要理解着去背，不必照章全背，既浪费时间又耽误自己的复习进度。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">同时，要理清楚每一章节内容的脉络，不要在答题时出现混乱，这样很容易因为答错题目所要求内容而失分。一定要注意重大会议以及国际实事，这是必考的内容。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">以上就是我简单的经验，时间字数有限，就不在此过多论述，希望对学弟学妹有帮助。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont,&amp; quot; Helvetica Neue&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; PingFang SC&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<p\r\n			style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n			<img class=\"\"\r\n				src=\"/upload/00000000028.png\" />\r\n		</p>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', null, null, '5', '3', null);
INSERT INTO `detail` VALUES ('18', '非学霸绕行的5所研究生院校，听说学渣从来不敢点开看', '1', '原哥工作室', '/upload/1526041131(1).jpg', '<section>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<section>中国人民大学</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<p\r\n				style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: inherit; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\">\r\n				<span\r\n					style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">新闻学院</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</section>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		class=\"\" height=\"143\" width=\"144\"\r\n		src=\"/upload/00000000030.png\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">中国人民大学新闻学院目前是教育部人文社会科学重点研究基地&quot;新闻与社会发展研究中心&quot;所在单位，是国家&quot;211&quot;工程和&quot;985&quot;工程重点建设单位。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">众学子中常言人大新闻学院甚为难考，令不少胆怯者望而生畏，那么报考人大新闻学院难度究竟几何？不妨稍作分析：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">学术型硕士</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">每年招生人数为20人左右，这意味着什么呢？人大新闻学院学术型硕士有四个专业方向，意味着有些专业方向可能录取不足五人。那么，每年报考学子总数大约多少呢？近年来大约为1000人，即招录比仅为50：1。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<strong\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(52, 149, 232);\">专业型硕士</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">人大新闻学院的专硕从2011年开始招生，每年的报考人数都在缓慢上升，招录比为12：1左右，而且专硕试题难度与学硕也有日渐接近的趋势。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><br /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<section>北京外国语大学</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<p\r\n					style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: inherit; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\">\r\n					<span\r\n						style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">高级翻译学院</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		class=\"\" height=\"181\" width=\"146\"\r\n		src=\"/upload/00000000031.png\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">想想从北外高翻出来的很大一部分同学是去联合国工作的，就该知道这个学院的研究生有多牛了吧。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">北外高翻所代表的是中国最顶尖的翻译学院，只招极少数人。关于难度，外界的说法各种不一，不过说的一致的都是难于上青天。其每年的报录比均在30:1左右，复试成绩占比高达70%。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<section>清华大学</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<p\r\n					style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: inherit; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\">\r\n					<span\r\n						style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">五道口金融学院</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		class=\"\" height=\"157\" width=\"157\"\r\n		src=\"/upload/00000000032.png\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">最近几年金融硕士很火，特别是清华北大这样的名校。五道口金融学院的前身又是中国人民银行研究生部，背景深厚，周小川为名誉院长，学术资源也蒸蒸日上，再加上清华的出国资源，五道口金融学院显得更加金贵。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们来看一下最近这两年的复试线。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">2018考研的复试线为370分，2017年的复试线为388分，虽然说逐年有所下降，但也还是只能静静地仰望。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">五道口金融学院毕业生的去向一般是一行三会（中国人民银行、证监会、保监会、银监会），各大银行总行，各大金融机构，券商，投资公司，外资银行等。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">中国金融还是处于初级发展阶段，对高端人才的需求量非常大，五道口这样深厚背景的学生就会显得特别突出。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<section>清华大学</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<p\r\n					style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: inherit; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\">\r\n					<span\r\n						style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">土木水利学院</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		class=\"\" height=\"157\" width=\"157\"\r\n		src=\"//upload/00000000032.png\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">没错，又是清华，土木工程是清华大学历史最悠久的系科之一。根据QS世界大学学科综合排名，清华大学土木学科（含水利和建设管理学科）2018年位居第五，2017年位居第五。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">清华传统工科的研究生一般对外招生人数都在个位数，而土木则更少，一般在4个左右。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">这里集中了大批土木界优秀的人才，同样也有很多像你一样各高校的牛人准备跃跃欲试并一显身手。所以，只有你具备了相当的实力，才有希望去拼博一下。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<section>\r\n		<section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<section>北京大学</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<section>\r\n				<p\r\n					style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: inherit; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\">\r\n					<span\r\n						style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">光华管理学院</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		class=\"\" height=\"148\" width=\"148\"\r\n		src=\"/upload/00000000033.png\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">最后，毋庸置疑，当属北大光华。有这么一句话，北大人怎么看光华，就和其他学校的人怎么看北大差不多。可见，要考上北大光华研究生的难度非同一般。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">北大光华的报录比一直在30:1左右。其次光华的专业课也很难拿高分，除非其他科目很高，所以选报的时候一定要慎重。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><br /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><img\r\n		src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_66.png?wx_lazy=1\"\r\n		class=\"\" /><img\r\n		src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_66.png?wx_lazy=1\"\r\n		class=\"\" /><img\r\n		src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_66.png?wx_lazy=1\"\r\n		class=\"\" /><img\r\n		src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_66.png?wx_lazy=1\"\r\n		class=\"\" /><img\r\n		src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_66.png?wx_lazy=1\"\r\n		class=\"\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">考研时的院校与专业选择不仅仅关乎考研的&quot;投入产出比&quot;，甚至从某种程度上决定了考研是否能够成功。因为某些学校的专业可能到目前为止还没有外校的学生跨校考研成功的先例，亦或者某些研究生导师压根不招跨专业报考的学生。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"margin: 0em 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp; quot; Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot; , &amp; quot; Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot; , Arial , sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span\r\n		style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">如果院校与专业的选择是错误的，那么你即使考了400分，这个结果也一样是失败的。就像房子设计图纸出了问题，施工再好，盖起来也绝对好不了，所以同学们在选择专业的时候一定要慎重。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', null, null, '5', '3', null);
INSERT INTO `detail` VALUES ('21', '有棱角的善良，才是真善良', '1', '原哥工作室', '/upload/65755d65-4a0e-4098-9767-3bd1ec9389fd.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://localhost:8081/upload/a48308fc-0b2b-4a45-b861-92d4f0153736.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#AB1942;\">善良是很珍贵的，但善良要是没有长出牙齿来，那就是软弱。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">我们都知道善良是一种美德，对人要和睦，处事要豁达。可是现在这个社会，越是善良，越是会变成被欺压的对象。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#595959;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">当一个人饥寒交迫的时候，你给他一碗米，就是解决了他的大问题，他会感恩不尽。但是，你如果不断的施舍，他就会觉得理所当然了。</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">人性都有贪婪的一面，时间久了，你的一碗米不够，二碗不够，三碗四碗还是堵不住他的口，尽心竭力也是杯水车薪。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">你要知道，这个世界，你若好到毫无保留，对方就敢坏到肆无忌惮。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://localhost:8081/upload/51e03854-d461-4494-a1ee-f9447df79237.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">心肠太软，容易被当软柿子捏；心眼太好，容易被当缺心眼看，最初的善意帮助，会变成最后的恶意后果。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">也许你行善布施，广集善德，举手之劳的小事并不会导致什么大的损失。然而君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#595959;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">当他的所求得不到满足，反咬一口时，你也最容易成为无辜的受伤者。</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#AB1942;\">没有棱角的善良，不仅不能向世界传达你的善意，反而输送了你的怯意；没有原则的善良，让真正的朋友寒心，让不值得的人永远不懂得“不可侵犯”四个大字。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">“你这么好，一定要帮我哦。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">“你这么好，一定不会拒绝我吧。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">很多时候我们都会听到这样的话。一些人出于面子，不好意思拒绝。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://localhost:8081/upload/66ec7545-e526-4035-96c2-440c77eaaec9.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">可是仔细想想我好，我就一定要帮你吗？何况我好，并不是我帮你的理由。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#595959;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">做一个有棱角有锋芒的善良人吧，懂得用智慧惩恶扬善，在好人那里还是好人，在坏人那里露出自己的锋芒和自己烈性。</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">人需要保持一颗善心是没有错，但不是对谁都好都没有底线，你没有底线，他们就没有原则。当善良失去原则的时候，就助长了恶。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#AB1942;\">有棱角的善良才是真善良，没有锋芒、没有棱角的人，是很难在这个粗鄙的世界走得更远。</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:17px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:15px;color:#595959;\">愿我们的善良，都带点锋芒。</span>\r\n</p>', '2018-05-11 23:38:00', '2018-05-11 23:38:00', '2', '3', null);
INSERT INTO `detail` VALUES ('22', '当先进青年，做优秀团干', '1', '黑科身边事', '/upload/607f0d07-8d96-4679-9b37-ff0b8fb4c10c.png', '<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/upload/e6c2e54d-f7ee-4277-a28c-5bdf53b24b08.png\" alt=\"\" /></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为加深团干部对基本团务的认识，提高团干部的综合素质，计算机与信息工程学院院团委在10月16日晚举办了团干部培训大会，共同促进，一同成长。</em><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"/upload/99b35bc5-e979-4429-b6bf-6cc8990033ce.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>计算机与信息工程学院团干培训大会</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em>&nbsp;</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为加深团干部对基本团务的认识，提高团干部的综合素质，计算机与信息工程学院院团委在10月16日晚举办了团干部培训大会，共同促进，一同成长。</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<em><img src=\"/upload/26168002-51f2-419a-8df7-d8144d82f5a8.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>团活督导部</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 主要负责检查本院团活及各院系公开团活开展情况，定期向校园委上报有关事宜，传达校园委的最新团活内容等工作2<strong>秘书部</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 主要负责加强团建工作，规范团籍管理：会议记录、健全和完善团委各项工作制度，根据各秘书长，上级团委的指示，制定全年的工作计划和总结，并督促各部门工作\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/upload/a613f3a7-2247-4f03-9217-404aa68170e8.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>新媒体建设部</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 新媒体工作主要包括“微博、微信、微视”，努力打造“三微一体”的新格局，网络信息平台的建设与维护，通过网络这一新媒介进行宣传推送消息\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '2018-05-12 07:13:55', '2018-05-12 07:13:55', '1', '4', null);
